event_required_for_event_type_check.name: event_required_for_event_type_check
event_required_for_event_type_check.value: (CASE WHEN "forms"."form_type" IN ('registration', 'evaluation') THEN "forms"."event_id" IS NOT NULL ELSE TRUE END)

eval_condition_required_for_eval_form_ch.name: eval_condition_required_for_eval_form_check
eval_condition_required_for_eval_form_ch.value: (CASE WHEN "forms"."form_type" = 'evaluation' THEN "forms"."evaluation_access_condition" IS NOT NULL ELSE TRUE END)

prompt_target_check.name: prompt_target_check
prompt_target_check.value:
(
        CASE WHEN "prompts"."event_id" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
        CASE WHEN "prompts"."agenda_item_id" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
        CASE WHEN "prompts"."form_id" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
      ) = 1
